==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aʊn|-aʊn]]

===Noun===
'''frown'''

# A facial expression in which the corners of the mouth are turned downward, usually indicating [[displeasure]] or [[disapproval]].

====Translations====
*Bosnian: [[namrštiti se]]
*Finnish: [[otsa]]n [[rypistys]], [[vihainen]] [[katse]]
