*Spanish: [[ceño]] {{m}}
*Portuguese: to frown = fazer cara feia
*Slovakian: [[mračiť sa]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{intransitive}}: To have a frown on one's face.
# {{intransitive}}: To express disapproval. (''Society frowns on fraud and theft.'')

